    "Unimodal Approaches for Disaster Analytics: Text-based disaster analysis has been extensively studied, particularly for high-resource languages.",
    "Caragea et al. [1] were the first to utilize CNN for differentiating between informational disaster messages, while transformer models like BERT, Devlin et al.",
